card.title: The Book of Arralan Season 2: The Prism

chapters.title: Life On The Seas With The Galley Girls

tracks.title: Life On The Seas With The Galley Girls

metadata.author: Morwenna Rose
metadata.description:
The children have found half of the crystals needed to restore The Prism, but three more still need finding. 

Just when they think they have met the most unusual that Arralan has to offer, they meet many more interesting folk along their way.
